Creating Map Legend 14

To create legend to map we should  down load the  file from top left corner  red button    unzip it  and save   image somewhere  on our local machine.

       - Go to insert > image> find image > Open

        - Place the image bottom right of the map.

    - Format

          Scaling > fit

        Title = on > Title Text = Low   <  > High, Font Color=Black,  Text Size = 11,  Alignment = Middle Font Family = Constantia

        Background = On> Color = White, transparency= 100%

       Lock space   = Off

      Border     = Off 

      Shadow      = On

     Action = Off

   Visual Heading = On 



How to create and format legends in a dashboard visuals ? Watch 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r9XnHmuWkZQ
